<MELItem itemNbr="21-22-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-22-01.1.2-21-22-01">
<Title>Flight Deck Boost Fan</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Fan is deactivated.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Air conditioning packs operate normally</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Note>
<Para>For an air conditioning pack to be operating normally, certain items associated with that system must operate normally.  See MEL item 21-51-01 for a list of those items.</Para>
</Note>
<Para>Deactivate flight deck boost fan (AMM DDG 21-22-01).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open circuit breaker FLT DECK BOOST FAN and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>